	"system": {
		"description": "<p>You are not just a student of magic, you are something of a prodigy, and you are certainly more enthusiastic than most. You gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li><p>Your Constitution, Wisdom, or Intelligence score increases by +1, to a maximum of 20.</p></li><li><p>You gain proficiency with the Arcana skill or an expertise die if you are already proficient. You also gain two free Arcana skill specialties that do not count against your skill specialties known.</p></li><li><p>You gain proficiency with two skills from the following list: Engineering, History, Investigation, Medicine, Nature, or Religion.</p></li><li><p>You gain an additional cantrip from the wizard spell list.</p></li><li><p>The gp and time costs to research rare spells are reduced by 20% for you.</p></li></ul>",
